<br>
I was in Marus Seru last evening, and decided to try a Fire Pet. I used the focus torch to summon, then decked him out in full phantom chain armor, 2 swords of runes, focus items &lt;to put for AC in the pet's other armor slots&gt;, plus an elemental shield for his back. Buffed him with BurnoutII, and expedience (just cause it was a new spell lol), and got ready to run for the zone if needed. Sent him out after a few things and WOW!!!<br>
<br>
Talk about a firecracker pet!!! He just ATE his way thru the lightcrawlers, zelniaks, and stonecrushers &lt;whatever they are called...the rock things&gt; like he was starving. Needed only a heal every so often, but he was just a monster. I made 30% into 29 last night in less than 3/4 of an hour! And without a mana spell regen either either <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I rarely dropped below 1/2 mana last night. My mana mostly went to throw a heal on Fluffy...and an occasional nuke on the mob. Broke my heart to reclaim him...but it was late and I needed to get to bed.<br>
<br>
I was just so shocked after struggling with my last level earth pet....(my research died every time I tried for the other pets, and I couldn't find anyone to research them for me. No one had any for sale either <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ugh suckage extreme) It was really amazing to see what powerful pets we can get!!! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I am looking forward to seeing what the other pets can do now as I rise higher in levels. I am sure it will get harder and more difficult as the higher in levels I gain, but for now...I am so very pleased with my new breed of Fluffies <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Just had to say, I LOVE being a mage!!! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
